x 1975\u20131976|Ted's Wedding]]\"\n|-\n| ''[[The Rookies]]''\n| Hap Dawson\n| Episode: \"[[List of The Rookies episodes|Reluctant Hero]]\"\n|-\n| ''[[Rhoda]]''\n| Vince Mazuma\n| Episode: \"[[List of Rhoda episodes|Chest Pains]]\"\n|-\n| rowspan=4|1976\n| ''[[Starsky & Hutch]]''\n| Tom Cole\n| Episode:  \"[[List of Starsky & Hutch episodes#Season 1 (1975\u201376)|The Hostages]]\"\n|-\n| ''[[Doc (1975 TV series)|Doc]]''\n| Jeff / George\n| Episode: \"A Little Bit of Soap\"\n|-\n| ''[[Rhoda]]''\n| Jerry Blocker\n| Episode: \"[[List of Rhoda episodes|Attack on Mr. Right]]\"\n|-\n| ''[[Phyllis (TV series)|Phyllis]]''\n| Paul Jameson\n| Episode: \"[[List of Phyllis episodes|The New Job]]\"\n|-\n| 1977\u20131984\n| ''[[Three's Company]]''\n| [[Jack Tripper]]\n| Lead role (174 episodes)\n|-\n| 1977, 1983\n| ''[[The Love Boat]]''\n| Dale Riley/Reinhardt / Ben Cummins\n| 2 episodes\n|-\n| rowspan=2|1978\n| ''[[Ringo (1978 film)|Ringo]]''\n| Marty\n| rowspan=2|TV film\n|-\n| ''Leave Yesterday Behind''\n| Paul Stallings\n|-\n| 1979\n| ''[[The Ropers]]''\n| [[Jack Tripper]]\n| Episode: \"[[The_Ropers#Episodes|The Party]]\"\n|-\n| rowspan=2|1980\n| ''[[The Associates (American TV series)|The Associates]]''\n| Chick\n| Episode: \"The Censors\"\n|-\n| ''[[The Comeback Kid (film)|The Comeback Kid]]''\n| Bubba Newman\n| TV film\n|-\n| 1981\n| ''[[Insight (TV series)|Insight]]''\n| Frankie\n| Episode: \"Little Miseries\"\n|-\n| rowspan=3|1982\n| ''[[Pray TV (1982 film)|Pray TV]]''\n| Tom McPherson\n| rowspan=2|TV film\n|-\n| ''In Love with an Older Woman''\n| Robert\n|-\n| ''[[The Fantastic Miss Piggy Show]]''\n| Himself\n| TV special\n|-\n| 1983\n| ''[[Sunset Limousine]]''\n| Alan O'Black\n| TV film\n|-\n| rowspan=2|1984\n| ''[[Love Thy Neighbor (1984 film)|Love Thy Neighbor]]''\n| Danny Loeb\n| TV film\n|-\n| ''[[Pryor's Place]]''\n| Himself\n| Episode: \"The Showoff\"\n|-\n| 1984\u20131985\n| ''[[Three's a Crowd]]''\n| [[Jack Tripper]]\n| Lead role (22 episodes)\n|-\n| 1985\n| ''Letting Go''\n| Alex\n| rowspan=3|TV film\n|-\n| rowspan=3|1986\n| ''Unnatural Causes''\n| Frank Coleman\n|-\n| ''[[A Smoky Mountain Christmas]]''\n| Judge Harold Benton\n| TV film\n|-\n| ''[[Life with Lucy]]''\n| Himself\n| Episode: \"[[Life_with_Lucy#Episodes|Lucy Makes a Hit with John Ritter]]\"\n|-\n| rowspan=2|1987\n| ''[[The Last Fling]]''\n| Phillip Reed\n| rowspan=2|TV film\n|-\n| ''[[Prison for Children]]''\n| David Royce\n|-\n| 1987\u20131989\n| ''[[Hooperman]]''\n| Det. Harry Hooperman\n| Lead role (42 episodes)\n|-\n| rowspan=2|1988\n| ''[[Mickey's 60th Birthday]]''\n| Dudley Goode\n| TV special\n|-\n| ''Tricks of the Trade''\n| Donald Todsen (cameo)\n| TV film\n|-\n| rowspan=2|1989\n| ''[[Have Faith]]''\n| Rick Shepherd\n| Episode: \"The Window\"\n|-\n| ''My Brother's Wife''\n| Barney\n| TV film\n|-\n| rowspan=2|1990\n| ''[[It (miniseries)|It]]''\n| [[It (novel)|Ben Hanscom]]\n| TV miniseries\n|-\n| ''[[The Dreamer of Oz: The L. Frank Baum Story]]''\n| [[L. Frank Baum]]\n| TV film\n|-\n| rowspan=3|1991\n| ''[[The Cosby Show]]''\n| Ray Evans\n| Episode: \"[[List of The Cosby Show episodes|Total Control]]\"\n|-\n| ''The Summer My Father Grew Up''\n| Paul\n| TV film\n|-\n| ''[[Anything but Love]]''\n| Patrick Serreau\n| Recurring role (5 episodes)\n|-\n| 1992\n| ''[[Fish Police (TV series)|Fish Police]]''\n| Inspector Gill (voice)\n| Lead role (6 episodes)\n|-\n| 1992\u20131995\n| ''[[Hearts Afire]]''\n| John Hartman\n| Lead role (54 episodes)\n|-\n| rowspan=3|1993\n| ''[[Heartbeat (1993 film)|Heartbeat]]''\n| Bill Grant\n| rowspan=2|TV film\n|-\n| ''The Only Way Out''\n| Jeremy Carlisle\n|-\n| ''[[The Larry Sanders Show]]''\n| Himself\n| Episode: \"[[List of The Larry Sanders Show episodes|Off Camera]]\"\n|-\n| 1994\n| ''[[Dave's World]]''\n| John Hartman\n| Episode: \"Please Won't You Be My Neighbor\"\n|-\n| rowspan=4|1995\n| ''Gramps''\n| Clarke MacGruder\n| rowspan=2|TV film\n|-\n| ''[[The Colony (1995 film)|The Colony]]''\n| Rick Knowlton\n|-\n| ''[[NewsRadio]]''\n| Dr. Frank Westford\n| Episode: \"[[List of NewsRadio episodes|The Shrink]]\"\n|-\n| ''[[The Larry Sanders Show]]''\n| Himself\n| Episode: \"[[List of The Larry Sanders Show episodes|The Fourteenth Floor]]\"\n|-\n| rowspan=4|1996\n| ''[[Unforgivable (1996 film)|Unforgivable]]''\n| Paul Hegstrom\n| TV film\n|-\n| ''[[Wings (1990 TV series)|Wings]]''\n| Stuart Davenport\n| Episode: \"[[List of Wings episodes|Love Overboard]]\"\n|-\n| ''[[For Hope]]''\n| Date #5\n| TV film (uncredited){{citation needed|date=July 2015}}\n|-\n| ''[[Touched by an Angel]]''\n| Mike O'Connor / Tom McKinsley\n| 2 episodes\n|-\n| rowspan=5|1997\n| ''Loss of Faith''\n| Bruce Simon Barker\n|rowspan=2|TV film\n|-\n| ''[[A Child's Wish]]''\n| Ed Chandler\n|-\n| ''[[Dead Man's Gun]]''\n| Harry McDonacle\n| Segment: \"The Great McDonacle\"\n|-\n| ''[[Over the Top (TV series)|Over the Top]]''\n| Justin Talbot\n| Episode: \"The Nemesis\"\n|-\n| ''[[Buffy the Vampire Slayer]]''\n| Ted Buchanan\n| Episode: \"[[Ted (Buffy the Vampire Slayer)|Ted]]\"\n|-\n| 1997\u20132004\n| ''[[King of the Hill]]''\n| Eugene Grandy (voice)\n| 4 episodes\n|-\n| rowspan=3|1998\n| ''Chance of a Lifetime''\n| Tom Maguire\n| TV film\n|-\n| ''[[Ally McBeal]]''\n| George Madison\n| 2 episodes\n|-\n| ''[[Dead Husbands]]''\n| Dr. Carter Elston\n| TV film\n|-\n| rowspan=4|1999\n| ''[[Veronica's Closet]]''\n| Tim\n| Episode: \"[[Veronica's Closet#Second season|Veronica's Favorite Year]]\"\n|-\n| ''Holy Joe''\n| Joe Cass\n| rowspan=3|TV film\n|-\n| ''[[It Came from the Sky]]''\n| Donald Bridges\n|-\n| ''[[Lethal Vows]]''\n| Dr. David Farris\n|-\n| 2000\u20132003\n| ''[[Clifford the Big Red Dog (TV series)|Clifford the Big Red Dog]]''\n| [[Clifford (character)|Clifford]] (voice)\n| 64 episodes\n|-\n| rowspan=3|2000\n| ''[[Chicago Hope]]''\n| Joe Dysmerski\n| Episode: \"[[List of Chicago Hope episodes|Simon Sez]]\"\n|-\n| ''[[Batman Beyond]]''\n| Dr. David Wheeler (voice)\n| Episode: \"[[List of Batman Beyond episodes#